overview: We are Orix Marketing. The provider of ultimate Internet Business Solutions. Driven by a visionary leadership team, a talented pool of designers, developers and futurists; We are excited about the world wide web and what it can do for business and people and we were formed in 2010, with the principal focus of offering reliable, industry-leading expertise in internet business solutions; we challenge the status quo of the industry each day. Orix Marketing is a young, spear headed multi-model internet Media Company creating new revelations in the Internet advertising space in Sri Lanka and it is the most advanced and targeted solution for all kind of e-solutions catering to small medium businesses to enterprise level.
